  26 Oct 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  pam_userdb-0.99.6.3.ebuild:
  Force -j1, does not build parallel (yes it's just a workaround).

  04 Oct 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
